<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١١١٠ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/598">إِسْحَاقُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3460">عَبْدُ الصَّمَدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1348">حَرْبٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6882">يَحْيَى </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1542">حَفْصُ بْنُ عُبَيْدِ اللهِ بْنِ أَنَسٍ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a><span class="special">﵁</span> حَدَّثَهُ: أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">«كَانَ يَجْمَعُ بَيْنَ هَاتَيْنِ الصَّلَاتَيْنِ فِي السَّفَرِ،<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> الْمَغْرِبَ وَالْعِشَاءَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>